# Helm Chart Conventions

## Bespoke
- **Deploy Scripts:** never add deployment automation (deploy.sh, install.sh, etc.) unless explicitly requested
- **Test Scripts:** never add testing frameworks or test scripts unless explicitly requested
- **Structure:** stick to standard Helm chart structure: Chart.yaml, values.yaml, templates/, and documentation
- **No Extras:** add what is specifically requested - no "helpful extras"
